summary: This Mod replaces the look from Cicero. Now he looks more as the Joker from the Batman-Comics.
descriptionHtml:
This Mod replaces the look from Cicero. Now he looks more then the Joker from the Batman-Comics. 

Installation:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Just Put the ESP and BSA Files in your Skyrim Data Folder and enable it with the Manager.

Deinstallation:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Erase the Cicer_Joker files from your Skyrim Data Folder.
author: LordDenethor
